HER MAJESTY QUEEN RAMBHAI BARNI OF SIAM BEING RECEIVED BY SIR FRANKLIN GIMSON ON HER ARRIVAL IN SINGAPORE

Description Edited by NAS:

Queen Rambhai Barni being received by Governor of Singapore Sir Franklin Gimson upon arrival in Singapore. The Queen was escorting the royal ashes of her husband, King Prajadhipok, back to Thailand from United Kingdom.
